{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":741,"text":"Sleep."},{"time":2383,"text":"It's something we spend about\na third of our lives doing,"},{"time":5204,"text":"but do any of us really understand what it's all about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8525,"text":"Two thousand years ago, Galen,"},{"time":10740,"text":"one of the most prominent medical researchers"},{"time":12880,"text":"of the ancient world,"},{"time":13939,"text":"proposed that while we're awake,"},{"time":16258,"text":"our brain's motive force, its juice,"},{"time":19620,"text":"would flow out to all the other parts of the body,"},{"time":22190,"text":"animating them but leaving the brain all dried up,"},{"time":26204,"text":"and he thought that when we sleep,"},{"time":27820,"text":"all this moisture that filled the rest of the body"},{"time":30358,"text":"would come rushing back,"},{"time":32102,"text":"rehydrating the brain"},{"time":33913,"text":"and refreshing the mind."},{"time":36459,"text":"Now, that sounds completely ridiculous to us now,"},{"time":38880,"text":"but Galen was simply trying to explain"},{"time":40921,"text":"something about sleep"},{"time":42528,"text":"that we all deal with every day."},{"time":45185,"text":"See, we all know based on our own experience"},{"time":47109,"text":"that when you sleep, it clears your mind,"},{"time":49821,"text":"and when you don't sleep,"},{"time":51283,"text":"it leaves your mind murky."},{"time":54210,"text":"But while we know a great deal more about sleep now"},{"time":56722,"text":"than when Galen was around,"},{"time":58526,"text":"we still haven't understood why it is that sleep,"},{"time":61406,"text":"of all of our activities, has this incredible"},{"time":64035,"text":"restorative function for the mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66754,"text":"So today I want to tell you about"},{"time":68254,"text":"some recent research"},{"time":69610,"text":"that may shed new light on this question."},{"time":72368,"text":"We've found that sleep may actually be"},{"time":75573,"text":"a kind of elegant design solution"},{"time":77946,"text":"to some of the brain's most basic needs,"},{"time":80523,"text":"a unique way that the brain"},{"time":82469,"text":"meets the high demands and the narrow margins"},{"time":85292,"text":"that set it apart from all the other organs of the body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90291,"text":"So almost all the biology that we observe"},{"time":93346,"text":"can be thought of as a series of problems"},{"time":95800,"text":"and their corresponding solutions,"},{"time":97841,"text":"and the first problem that every organ must solve"},{"time":101321,"text":"is a continuous supply of nutrients to fuel"},{"time":103819,"text":"all those cells of the body."},{"time":105560,"text":"In the brain, that is especially critical;"},{"time":108138,"text":"its intense electrical activity uses up"},{"time":110355,"text":"a quarter of the body's entire energy supply,"},{"time":113213,"text":"even though the brain accounts"},{"time":114843,"text":"for only about two percent of the body's mass."},{"time":118180,"text":"So the circulatory system"},{"time":119792,"text":"solves the nutrient delivery problem"},{"time":122223,"text":"by sending blood vessels to supply nutrients"},{"time":124763,"text":"and oxygen to every corner of our body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128106,"text":"You can actually see it in this video here."},{"time":131120,"text":"Here, we're imaging blood vessels"},{"time":132702,"text":"in the brain of a living mouse."},{"time":135597,"text":"The blood vessels form a complex network"},{"time":138117,"text":"that fills the entire brain volume."},{"time":140465,"text":"They start at the surface of the brain,"},{"time":142266,"text":"and then they dive down into the tissue itself,"},{"time":145147,"text":"and as they spread out, they supply nutrients"},{"time":147508,"text":"and oxygen to each and every cell in the brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153276,"text":"Now, just as every cell requires"},{"time":156246,"text":"nutrients to fuel it,"},{"time":158137,"text":"every cell also produces waste as a byproduct,"},{"time":161277,"text":"and the clearance of that waste"},{"time":162823,"text":"is the second basic problem"},{"time":165090,"text":"that each organ has to solve."},{"time":167882,"text":"This diagram shows the body's lymphatic system,"},{"time":170465,"text":"which has evolved to meet this need."},{"time":172895,"text":"It's a second parallel network of vessels"},{"time":175707,"text":"that extends throughout the body."},{"time":177721,"text":"It takes up proteins and other waste"},{"time":179678,"text":"from the spaces between the cells,"},{"time":181602,"text":"it collects them, and then dumps them into the blood"},{"time":184414,"text":"so they can be disposed of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186675,"text":"But if you look really closely at this diagram,"},{"time":188464,"text":"you'll see something"},{"time":189858,"text":"that doesn't make a lot of sense."},{"time":192186,"text":"So if we were to zoom into this guy's head,"},{"time":194943,"text":"one of the things that you would see there"},{"time":197136,"text":"is that there are no lymphatic vessels in the brain."},{"time":201298,"text":"But that doesn't make a lot of sense, does it?"},{"time":204392,"text":"I mean, the brain is this intensely active organ"},{"time":207597,"text":"that produces a correspondingly\nlarge amount of waste"},{"time":210162,"text":"that must be efficiently cleared."},{"time":212739,"text":"And yet, it lacks lymphatic vessels, which means that"},{"time":215701,"text":"the approach that the rest of the body takes"},{"time":217497,"text":"to clearing away its waste"},{"time":219482,"text":"won't work in the brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222491,"text":"So how, then, does the brain solve"},{"time":224539,"text":"its waste clearance problem?"},{"time":226293,"text":"Well, that seemingly mundane question"},{"time":229982,"text":"is where our group first jumped into this story,"},{"time":233390,"text":"and what we found"},{"time":235411,"text":"as we dove down into the brain,"},{"time":237746,"text":"down among the neurons and the blood vessels,"},{"time":240637,"text":"was that the brain's solution"},{"time":242820,"text":"to the problem of waste clearance,"},{"time":245383,"text":"it was really unexpected."},{"time":247200,"text":"It was ingenious,"},{"time":250050,"text":"but it was also beautiful."},{"time":253168,"text":"Let me tell you about what we found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254835,"text":"So the brain has this large pool"},{"time":257389,"text":"of clean, clear fluid called cerebrospinal fluid."},{"time":260850,"text":"We call it the CSF."},{"time":262169,"text":"The CSF fills the space that surrounds the brain,"},{"time":266149,"text":"and wastes from inside the brain"},{"time":267672,"text":"make their way out to the CSF,"},{"time":269894,"text":"which gets dumped, along with \nthe waste, into the blood."},{"time":273157,"text":"So in that way, it sounds a lot like"},{"time":274277,"text":"the lymphatic system, doesn't it?"},{"time":276869,"text":"But what's interesting is that the fluid and the waste"},{"time":279625,"text":"from inside the brain,"},{"time":281357,"text":"they don't just percolate their way randomly"},{"time":283764,"text":"out to these pools of CSF."},{"time":286138,"text":"Instead, there is a specialized network of plumbing"},{"time":289861,"text":"that organizes and facilitates this process."},{"time":293753,"text":"You can see that in these videos."},{"time":295902,"text":"Here, we're again imaging into the brain"},{"time":298940,"text":"of living mice."},{"time":300424,"text":"The frame on your left shows"},{"time":302347,"text":"what's happening at the brain's surface,"},{"time":304406,"text":"and the frame on your right shows"},{"time":305970,"text":"what's happening down below the surface of the brain"},{"time":307916,"text":"within the tissue itself."},{"time":309639,"text":"We've labeled the blood vessels in red,"},{"time":311898,"text":"and the CSF that's surrounding the brain"},{"time":313922,"text":"will be in green."},{"time":315745,"text":"Now, what was surprising to us"},{"time":317545,"text":"was that the fluid on the outside of the brain,"},{"time":320796,"text":"it didn't stay on the outside."},{"time":323608,"text":"Instead, the CSF was pumped back into"},{"time":327011,"text":"and through the brain"},{"time":328884,"text":"along the outsides of the blood vessels,"},{"time":331916,"text":"and as it flushed down into the brain"},{"time":334300,"text":"along the outsides of these vessels,"},{"time":336100,"text":"it was actually helping to clear away,"},{"time":338912,"text":"to clean the waste from the spaces"},{"time":341353,"text":"between the brain's cells."},{"time":344199,"text":"If you think about it,"},{"time":346111,"text":"using the outsides of these blood vessels like this"},{"time":349588,"text":"is a really clever design solution,"},{"time":352107,"text":"because the brain is enclosed"},{"time":354829,"text":"in a rigid skull"},{"time":356652,"text":"and it's packed full of cells,"},{"time":358755,"text":"so there is no extra space inside it"},{"time":361500,"text":"for a whole second set of vessels\nlike the lymphatic system."},{"time":365100,"text":"Yet the blood vessels,"},{"time":366359,"text":"they extend from the surface of the brain"},{"time":368317,"text":"down to reach every single cell in the brain,"},{"time":370926,"text":"which means that fluid"},{"time":372164,"text":"that's traveling along the outsides of these vessels"},{"time":375460,"text":"can gain easy access to the entire brain's volume,"},{"time":379260,"text":"so it's actually this really clever way"},{"time":381444,"text":"to repurpose one set of vessels, the blood vessels,"},{"time":385209,"text":"to take over and replace the function"},{"time":387998,"text":"of a second set of vessels, the lymphatic vessels,"},{"time":391181,"text":"to make it so you don't need them."},{"time":393592,"text":"And what's amazing is that no other organ"},{"time":395909,"text":"takes quite this approach"},{"time":397550,"text":"to clearing away the waste from between its cells."},{"time":400610,"text":"This is a solution that is entirely unique to the brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406430,"text":"But our most surprising finding"},{"time":408698,"text":"was that all of this,"},{"time":410801,"text":"everything I just told you about,"},{"time":413151,"text":"with all this fluid rushing through the brain,"},{"time":416469,"text":"it's only happening in the sleeping brain."},{"time":420653,"text":"Here, the video on the left"},{"time":422103,"text":"shows how much of the CSF is moving"},{"time":424364,"text":"through the brain of a living mouse while it's awake."},{"time":427970,"text":"It's almost nothing."},{"time":429843,"text":"Yet in the same animal,"},{"time":431418,"text":"if we wait just a little while until it's gone to sleep,"},{"time":434623,"text":"what we see is that the CSF"},{"time":437380,"text":"is rushing through the brain,"},{"time":439798,"text":"and we discovered that at the same time"},{"time":441958,"text":"when the brain goes to sleep,"},{"time":444570,"text":"the brain cells themselves seem to shrink,"},{"time":447233,"text":"opening up spaces in between them,"},{"time":449270,"text":"allowing fluid to rush through"},{"time":451407,"text":"and allowing waste to be cleared out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454140,"text":"So it seems that Galen may actually have been"},{"time":456654,"text":"sort of on the right track when he wrote about"},{"time":458910,"text":"fluid rushing through the brain"},{"time":461610,"text":"when sleep came on."},{"time":463252,"text":"Our own research, now it's 2,000 years later,"},{"time":466705,"text":"suggests that what's happening is that"},{"time":468775,"text":"when the brain is awake"},{"time":470834,"text":"and is at its most busy,"},{"time":472948,"text":"it puts off clearing away the waste"},{"time":475310,"text":"from the spaces between its cells until later,"},{"time":478381,"text":"and then, when it goes to sleep"},{"time":480240,"text":"and doesn't have to be as busy,"},{"time":482588,"text":"it shifts into a kind of cleaning mode"},{"time":485165,"text":"to clear away the waste"},{"time":486852,"text":"from the spaces between its cells,"},{"time":488360,"text":"the waste that's accumulated throughout the day."},{"time":490777,"text":"So it's actually a little bit like how you or I,"},{"time":493185,"text":"we put off our household chores during the work week"},{"time":496267,"text":"when we don't have time to get to it,"},{"time":497729,"text":"and then we play catch up on all\nthe cleaning that we have to do"},{"time":500990,"text":"when the weekend rolls around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503748,"text":"Now, I've just talked a lot about waste clearance,"},{"time":507020,"text":"but I haven't been very specific"},{"time":508472,"text":"about the kinds of waste"},{"time":509866,"text":"that the brain needs to be clearing"},{"time":512161,"text":"during sleep in order to stay healthy."},{"time":514704,"text":"The waste product that these recent studies"},{"time":516301,"text":"focused most on is amyloid-beta,"},{"time":518719,"text":"which is a protein that's made\nin the brain all the time."},{"time":521914,"text":"My brain's making amyloid-beta right now,"},{"time":523772,"text":"and so is yours."},{"time":525930,"text":"But in patients with Alzheimer's disease,"},{"time":527932,"text":"amyloid-beta builds up and aggregates"},{"time":530531,"text":"in the spaces between the brain's cells,"},{"time":532544,"text":"instead of being cleared away \nlike it's supposed to be,"},{"time":535970,"text":"and it's this buildup of amyloid-beta"},{"time":537980,"text":"that's thought to be one of the key steps"},{"time":540193,"text":"in the development of that terrible disease."},{"time":542814,"text":"So we measured how fast amyloid-beta is cleared"},{"time":545908,"text":"from the brain when it's awake"},{"time":547640,"text":"versus when it's asleep,"},{"time":549418,"text":"and we found that indeed,"},{"time":551296,"text":"the clearance of amyloid-beta"},{"time":553186,"text":"is much more rapid from the sleeping brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557705,"text":"So if sleep, then,"},{"time":559384,"text":"is part of the brain's solution"},{"time":561342,"text":"to the problem of waste clearance,"},{"time":563352,"text":"then this may dramatically change how we think"},{"time":565728,"text":"about the relationship between sleep,"},{"time":567963,"text":"amyloid-beta, and Alzheimer's disease."},{"time":571319,"text":"A series of recent clinical studies"},{"time":573277,"text":"suggest that among patients"},{"time":575110,"text":"who haven't yet developed Alzheimer's disease,"},{"time":578204,"text":"worsening sleep quality and sleep duration"},{"time":581270,"text":"are associated with a greater amount"},{"time":583288,"text":"of amyloid-beta building up in the brain,"},{"time":586100,"text":"and while it's important to point out"},{"time":587967,"text":"that these studies don't prove"},{"time":589677,"text":"that lack of sleep or poor sleep"},{"time":591866,"text":"cause Alzheimer's disease,"},{"time":594273,"text":"they do suggest that the failure of the brain"},{"time":596883,"text":"to keep its house clean"},{"time":598795,"text":"by clearing away waste like amyloid-beta"},{"time":601551,"text":"may contribute to the development"},{"time":603453,"text":"of conditions like Alzheimer's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607070,"text":"So what this new research tells us, then,"},{"time":608975,"text":"is that the one thing that all of you"},{"time":611302,"text":"already knew about sleep,"},{"time":612710,"text":"that even Galen understood about sleep,"},{"time":615363,"text":"that it refreshes and clears the mind,"},{"time":618434,"text":"may actually be a big part"},{"time":619975,"text":"of what sleep is all about."},{"time":622292,"text":"See, you and I, we go to sleep"},{"time":623810,"text":"every single night,"},{"time":625543,"text":"but our brains, they never rest."},{"time":628546,"text":"While our body is still"},{"time":630380,"text":"and our mind is off walking in dreams somewhere,"},{"time":633451,"text":"the elegant machinery of the brain"},{"time":635127,"text":"is quietly hard at work"},{"time":637107,"text":"cleaning and maintaining"},{"time":639300,"text":"this unimaginably complex machine."},{"time":642135,"text":"Like our housework,"},{"time":643176,"text":"it's a dirty and a thankless job,"},{"time":645925,"text":"but it's also important."},{"time":648180,"text":"In your house, if you stop cleaning your kitchen"},{"time":650583,"text":"for a month,"},{"time":652491,"text":"your home will become completely unlivable"},{"time":654930,"text":"very quickly."},{"time":656537,"text":"But in the brain, the consequences"},{"time":658625,"text":"of falling behind may be much greater"},{"time":661556,"text":"than the embarrassment of dirty countertops,"},{"time":664284,"text":"because when it comes to cleaning the brain,"},{"time":666848,"text":"it is the very health and function"},{"time":669224,"text":"of the mind and the body that's at stake,"},{"time":672169,"text":"which is why understanding these"},{"time":674410,"text":"very basic housekeeping functions of the brain today"},{"time":678682,"text":"may be critical for preventing and treating"},{"time":681675,"text":"diseases of the mind tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684703,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686751,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}